{"tid":500350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑虐待貓個案","createTime":"2017-12-15T16:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T16:35:48.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"04c8dff3ce87d4cbf25962038de3d43a6d3e9259","tid":500350,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的，懷疑有人虐待貓見下圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/003444_8e45c214c8ea0d2d4df486487e6dc084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F003444_8e45c214c8ea0d2d4df486487e6dc084.jpg&h=03d52230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻貓好慘啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f9522b93c8a8f02d4c71a479fb8aecd4fe313e","tid":500350,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"這個女人之前死左隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bi.luk.77/posts/10153693148787789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbi.luk.77%2Fposts%2F10153693148787789&d=OC%2BRaEXVmetbwMqEMhrBI26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7e6834af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bi.luk.77/posts/10153693148787789</a><br />\n<br />\n30-11-2015<br />\n剔剔離開左我，去了天國，做隻快樂的小天使！<br />\n因為我嘅疏忽，剔剔食左我條針線！<br />\n因為我嘅猶疑不決，錯過了剔剔最佳嘅治療時機！睇住佢病，睇住佢痛，確實令我好心痛！<br />\n本以為手術後佢實無事，尋晚見佢仲好精靈，仲識發脾氣，點知都係撐唔住。。。<br />\n我真係無依個心理準備。。。<br />\n一條線，帶走了我的寶貝剔，依樣係我<br />\n萬萬都想唔到，可惜真係發生了。。。<br />\n今日診所打黎告知我剔剔走了，即時淚水一發不可收拾，已經喊左成日，但眼淚就好似缺堤一樣冇打算停。。。<br />\n我無法帶剔剔返屋企！<br />\n好多嘅回憶。。。剔剔每天回家對著我喵喵叫，鐘意引你注意，鐘意玩橡筋，鐘意衝門，鐘意瞓大脾的淘氣貓，可惜如今已不再復見！<br />\n好多的點解。。。點解我要車衫，點解我唔掃乾淨D線，點解會俾剔剔食左條線，點解唔早D開刀，點解。。。<br />\n後悔，內疚，我真係好唔捨得。。。依個慘痛嘅教訓我實在承受唔起。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/12279006_10153693148537789_5455258088547329656_n.jpg?oh=f090259f16834b7070d12eb099afcea3&amp;oe=5AC900E6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F12279006_10153693148537789_5455258088547329656_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df090259f16834b7070d12eb099afcea3%26oe%3D5AC900E6&h=c06348de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f07c51ddfd21248b169fbcb6174d0dcc52615ca","tid":500350,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"9c4e28964ec921014c4fda99b375d0bad7429ef0","tid":500350,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報警</blockquote><br />\n報左？"},{"pid":"e7ccf9dff03ac4a8271d4449d3e15043792272d9","tid":500350,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ff1169350096236390ae2e3f93bcc25de0f0b47","tid":500350,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"下次開係寵物台"}]}